    "text": "Terminating Reckless and Unnecessary Checks Known to Erode Regular Shipping Act or the TRUCKERS Act\n\nThis bill prohibits the Department of Homeland Security from imposing any COVID-19 vaccination requirement on any commercial truck driver who is a national of Canada or Mexico and seeking to temporarily enter the United States for business through a land port of entry."
